About the eHR Engineering Team
The eHR Engineering team is part of ByteDance Enterprise Services team. We are a rapidly growing and highly capable team. We are builders who embraces change, push boundaries, committed to promoting the revolution of human resources process informatization. We build a highly efficient development engine for ByteDance and bring our products to millions of professionals outside ByteDance by making these available on a SaaS Platform. As a member of People, you play a key role in re-shaping the productivity of the HR industry with the global team. We are looking for talented individuals to join us in 2021 - people who want to inspire creativity and co-create the future with us. Responsibilities
1. Write and review code and debug problems to develop an SaaS product to solve the complex problems from global clients;
2. Apply knowledge gained in computer science courses to build next generation systems to constantly be at the cutting edge.

Qualifications
1... Final year or recent graduate with a background in Software Development, Computer Science, Computer Engineering, Information Systems or a related technical discipline;
2. Experience in Software Development and coding in a general purpose programming language is a plus;
3. Agile, quick self learner, highly self-motivated and quick problem-solving capabilities;
4. Possess good coding skills, data structure and basic algorithm skills. Application
1. Applications will be reviewed on a rolling basis and we encourage you to apply early;
2. Interview starts from February 2021
